<br>
I played a Rogue into the Tier 2 game on another server (we were up to NToV and Velious Kings level) and usually when I gained aggro for any length of time I would die. I started to notice this around 48 or so in Karnor's castle. Before, I could take a bit of pounding and still be ok, but at around 48, the mobs start to hit so fast and hard that you will drain the cleric's mana always having to heal you.<br>
<br>
Now, this isn't a 100% truth, it is possible for a Rogue to tank just like it's possible for a Rogue to solo, it's just not as practical as fulfilling your role as a sneaky, attacking from shadows damage dealer who tries to not attract attention. I would think that in Sebilis, a tanking rogue would die. The cleric couldn't heal you fast enough when you pull 3 frogs before the chanter could mez them all unless you had extreme high end +AC and +HP gear.<br>
<br>
Now about the shield - you would be decreasing your damage output by about 2/3 by tanking anyways (no backstabs and no offhand if you use a shield) so your killing would be rather slow and you would be a constant drain and irritation on the Cleric (Superior Heal and Celest Heal isn't quite enough and CHeal is overkill). The extra 25AC wouldn't help you get hit that much less to really make a difference when things are quadding for 100+ a hit.<br>
<br>
These are just my experiences - the Bladestopper is a Cleric and Shaman shield IMHO. Pallies and SK could use it also, but due to the high availability of great ratio 2hs weapons out there for a good price, I would think they would rather go 2h than 1h+shield with a few exceptions.<br>
Vulrath <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/utitaisia.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Titaisia</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Wishful Dreamer</span><br>  Posts: 135<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(10/2/02 10:35:49 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2838.topic&index=1>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Rogues tanking (to Siffo)</span><hr size=1> ((I am in Saga with Siffo, so I will jump in and say thank you for the advice to him!  ^_^<br>
<br>
