<br>
I think the kind of meanies he is looking at fighting is probably things like Great Divide giants, and things like that.  He doesn't want to be tank in his level range, but he can probably manage to take hits better than a level 34 or so ranger he might be fighting with.  I think that is the situation he is in.  He will probably be keeping aggro most of the time, anyway, I think.  (Correct me if I am wrong, Siffo?)<br>
<br>
In that context, with him fighting less powerful meanies and tanking for his weaker groupmates, would the shield save the druid healer any mana, or would the longer fights (from not stabbing, most likely from the front, with both weapons) use up any benefit of the extra armor?<br>
