Jarkell Ravensteel <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/usiffo.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Siffo</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Silly old Rogue</span><br>  Posts: 202<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(10/5/02 7:12:36 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2838.topic&index=11>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Tanky rogues</span><hr size=1> Hide and Sneak are both 200<br>
<br>
I don't have a tank or I wouldn'd need to be tanking.<br>
<br>
